Name: Roboggled
About the game: Welcome to the world of Roboggled where you play as a little robot who needs to figure out how to deliver a crate to its drop point. Sound easy? You'll also need to use or avoid the environment in order to solve each puzzle, which includes lasers, conveyor belts, mirrors, teleporters and more! - Contains 60 levels. - Includes a level editor. - Play levels created by others. - Upload your levels to share them with others. (Must create an account and be logged in)
